This pilot early phase I trial studies the Automated Device for Asthma Monitoring and Management in monitoring adult patients with lung cancer who are undergoing radiation therapy.

 The Automated Device for Asthma Monitoring and Management may provide useful information to doctors to help monitor adult patients with lung cancer and diagnose certain conditions earlier than traditional means.

